note over browser:
user types text into text field,
and clicks the submit button
end note

note over browser:
browser calls form's onsubmit handler which:
1. prevents default action
2. creates new note and adds to note list
3. browser rerenders note list
4. browser sends new note to server
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
